[{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8194-ac09-c557361ed3f7","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-8185-b5e4-c2c90ca76856"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T20:54:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T20:54:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"The MX320V is MAXAM's mixed service drive tire, engineered for severe mixed service applications such as waste, cement, and gravel. With a 230mm tread width promoting stability and even wear, the MX320V offers maximum durability for the rigors of high scrub applications. Its lug pattern strikes a balance between traction and wear on various surfaces, providing versatility in different environments. With its reinforced abrasion-resistant compound, this tire boasts a low-rolling resistance and unrivaled performance with cut, chip, and abrasion-resistance. The MX320V is designed for mixed service applications such as waste, cement, and gravel. Available only in North America","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"The MX320V is MAXAM's mixed service drive tire, engineered for severe mixed service applications such as waste, cement, and gravel. With a 230mm tread width promoting stability and even wear, the MX320V offers maximum durability for the rigors of high scrub applications. Its lug pattern strikes a balance between traction and wear on various surfaces, providing versatility in different environments. With its reinforced abrasion-resistant compound, this tire boasts a low-rolling resistance and unrivaled performance with cut, chip, and abrasion-resistance. The MX320V is designed for mixed service applications such as waste, cement, and gravel. Available only in North Amer